    <section class="kairos-section kairos-section--dark"><div class="kairos-shell kairos-split"><div><p class="kairos-eyebrow">Experience First</p><h2>Less searching. Less repetition. More forward movement.</h2><p>Kairos is designed to reduce prompt memorization, fragmented tools, repeated explanations, and workflow interruptions. The experience centers on objectives, visible progress, and successful completion.</p></div><div class="kairos-principles"><article><strong>Objective-first interaction</strong><span>Begin with what needs to be accomplished.</span></article><article><strong>Authoritative context</strong><span>Use approved standards and preserved project knowledge.</span></article><article><strong>Visible momentum</strong><span>Show completed assets, milestones, and next steps.</span></article><article><strong>Human approval where required</strong><span>Preserve executive and customer control at important boundaries.</span></article></div></div></section>
